org.firebirdsql.gds

Interface ServiceRequestBuffer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Parameter>, ParameterBuffer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ServiceRequestBufferImp

    public interface ServiceRequestBuffer
extends ParameterBuffer
    Instance of this interface represents a Service Request Buffer from the Firebird API documentation and specifies the attributes for the Services API operation.

        static final int ACTION_BACKUP
        ********************************************************************** Operations that can be called via Services API. There are following groups of operations:

        - backup/restore - database repair - user management - changing the database properties - license management - database and server information
